{"tid":1580087,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"貼連儂牆被檢控","createTime":"2019-09-19T01:42:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T04:29:50.000Z","uid":73910,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b424bbdd31d5783e1d73d3e3f39fbef9363c9111","tid":1580087,"uid":73910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T01:42:46.000Z","msg":"首宗貼反修例物品票控個案 青衣黐海報年輕男女提堂<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xoYoGWV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxoYoGWV.jpg&h=3ee9de84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5flfYAHTsiVLqq1%2Bkbj60LM%3D&h=d4ca8537\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】修例風波爆發後，連儂牆在各區萌生。一對年輕男女涉嫌在青衣街頭上張貼3幅反修例的政治海報，被警方票控在政府土地未經准許展示海報。案件今(18日)在西九龍裁判法院提堂，被告暫毋須答辯，裁判官把案件押至10月16日，以便控辯雙方索取文件及辯方向被告提供法律意見。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指，男子何志程及女子郭曉楠違反《公眾衞生及市政條例》第104A條，即在政府土地上未獲得主管當局書面准許，而展示或張貼招貼或海報。案情指，該男女於8月5日下午6時20分，在青衣青荃路旁的欄杆張貼了3張1米乘0.4米的海報。<br />\n<br />\n據知，本案是首宗市民因張貼反修例海報而被票控的案件。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/hk.news.yahoo.com/amphtml/%25E9%25A6%2596%25E5%25AE%2597%25E8%25B2%25BC%25E5%258F%258D%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E7%2589%25A9%25E5%2593%2581%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E6%258E%25A7%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E9%259D%2592%25E8%25A1%25A3%25E9%25BB%2590%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25BC%2595%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E6%258F%2590%25E5%25A0%2582-083420991.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2Famphtml%2F%2525E9%2525A6%252596%2525E5%2525AE%252597%2525E8%2525B2%2525BC%2525E5%25258F%25258D%2525E4%2525BF%2525AE%2525E4%2525BE%25258B%2525E7%252589%2525A9%2525E5%252593%252581%2525E7%2525A5%2525A8%2525E6%25258E%2525A7%2525E5%252580%25258B%2525E6%2525A1%252588-%2525E9%25259D%252592%2525E8%2525A1%2525A3%2525E9%2525BB%252590%2525E6%2525B5%2525B7%2525E5%2525A0%2525B1%25